{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Window.performance","mdn_url":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/performance_property","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/performance_property\"><code>Performance_property</code></a></strong></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<div id=\"sect2\">A API Web Performance permite páginas da web acessarem algumas funções para medir a performance de páginas e aplicações da web, incluindo a API Navigation Timing e dados&nbsp;de tempo de alta resolução.</div>\n\n<div id=\"sect3\">&nbsp;</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"methods","title":"Métodos","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"performance.mark_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Performance/mark\"><code>performance.mark()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Mapeia um&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMHighResTimeStamp\"><code>DOMHighResTimeStamp</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> para o nome especificado representando a quantidade de milissegundos passados desde um momento de referência.</dd>\n</dl>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"performance.now\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Performance/now\" title=\"performance.now()\"><code>performance.now()</code></a></dt>\n <dd>Retorna um&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMHighResTimeStamp\"><code>DOMHighResTimeStamp</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> representando a quantidade de milissegundos passados desde um momento de referência.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"properties","title":"Propriedades","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"performance.timing_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Performance/timing\"><code>performance.timing</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>É um objeto&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PerformanceTiming\"><code>PerformanceTiming</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>&nbsp;contendo informações de performance relacionadas a latência.</dd>\n <dt id=\"performance.navigation_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Performance/navigation\"><code>performance.navigation</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>É um objeto&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PerformanceNavigation\"><code>PerformanceNavigation</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> representando o tipo de navegação que ocorre no contexto de navegação dado, como a quantidade de redirecionamentos necessários para&nbsp;buscar o recurso.</dd>\n <dt id=\"performance.memory\"><a href=\"https://docs.webplatform.org/wiki/apis/timing/properties/memory\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">performance.memory</a></dt>\n <dd>Uma extensao não-padrão adicionada ao Chrome.</dd>\n</dl>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Métodos","id":"methods"},{"text":"Propriedades","id":"properties"}],"summary":"","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Window.performance","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"self.performance","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Window.performance","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Window.performance","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Window.performance","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/api/performance_property","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/web/api/performance_property/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web","title":"Tecnologia Web para desenvolvedores"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API","title":"APIs da Web"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/performance_property","title":"Window.performance"}],"pageTitle":"Window.performance - APIs da Web | MDN","noIndexing":false}}